pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Plant Omega 3 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

EPA & DHA derived from sustainably sourced marine algae
to support brain and heart health.

Wanderlust Plant Omega-3 is a consciously created, vegan, plant active source of EPA & DHA derived from sustainably sourced marine algae. DHA supports cognitive function, brain and pregnancy health. EPA & DHA supports heart health and nervous system function.

Size: 30 Capsules

Warnings

Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy; particularly in your first trimester.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
DHA/EPA rich schizochytrium algal oil 962.7 mg
Equiv. docosahexaenoic acid (DHA)-------300 mg
Equiv. eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) ------- 150 mg

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Cognitive Function, Brain Health & Nervous System Health: Take one capsule daily.

Heart Health: Take two capsules daily.

Pregnancy Health: Take two capsules daily,

With a main meal or as directed by your healthcare practitioner.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C away from direct heat and sunlight. Do not use if cap seal or
inner seal is missing or broken.
